pr_title: [GSoC] Adding Different Preview Options To The Designer
pr_body: This summer I have worked on improving the MockForm by adding three different preview options in the Designer. The preview options are Android Material (Android 5+), Android Holo (Android 3.0-4.4.2) and introducing the new iPhone/iPad (iOS 13) MockForm so that users can preview their apps and get to know how it will look on different platforms.
